Flagship product: Qybala v1 — an AI-powered, tarot-inspired self-reflection app, currently pre-seed stage
Dan-George is a former Google Staff Engineer with 10+ years scaling systems to billions of users (YouTube Ads, Search Ads)
Currently pursuing MSc in Psychology & Neuroscience of Mental Health at King's College London
